  <p>Yet another (S)CSS / jQuery component library.</p>

  <p>Since 2014 Codebase and these docs have been added to and overhauled whenever.</p>

  <p>As of v.1 Codebase somewhat follows the <a href="http://getbem.com/">BEM</a> naming methodology for its mixins and classes.</p>

  <p>All layout, utilities and components have been created first as <code>@mixin</code>s and then classes have been built from these mixins.</p>

  <p>So although the docs demonstrate the Codebase classes, SCSS users can also <code>@include</code> Codebase mixins in their own mixins and classes.</p>

  <p>All the Codebase <code>!default</code> variables can be easily overridden.</p>

